{"tid":2419832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸據報有遊行支持軍方 軍方稱要恢復國家經濟","createTime":"2021-02-23T13:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T17:20:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"36b0ce8966e5f926e9e4f685c20dab29a3f5b764","tid":2419832,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:51:42.000Z","msg":"緬甸多個城市繼續有民眾抗議軍事政變，但人數較星期一減少，據報亦有人參與遊行支持軍方。<br />\n<br />\n國際社會持續向緬甸軍方施壓，七國集團外長發表聲明，譴責緬甸當局鎮壓反對政變的人，又說會追究以暴力對待和平示威者人士的責任。美國宣布再制裁兩名緬甸軍政府成員。歐盟亦正考慮制裁軍方擁有的企業。<br />\n<br />\n面對西方制裁，官方傳媒引述國防軍總司令敏昂萊在政府會議上表示，要將精力投入在恢復身陷困境的國家經濟，必須採取補救措施，呼籲減少國家支出和進口，並擴大出口。他又說，警方正使用最低武力應對示威，例如橡膠子彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577068-20210223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577068-20210223.htm&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a5b64b62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577068-20210223.htm&h=432bc656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577068-20210223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bc4d4ec4b5022bf90753daaec521e04a01a6af73","tid":2419832,"uid":240036,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"照抄香港藍絲無誤"},{"pid":"10e90765940d9910557c5bf56b643bee7c589371","tid":2419832,"uid":65888,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"永遠都係用經濟做藉口，你話呢單野支那無份都無人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334465a9975e5173d44ea27bb22541cf90a6f3bd","tid":2419832,"uid":52779,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"10e90765940d9910557c5bf56b643bee7c589371","tid":2419832,"uid":65888,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"永遠都係用經濟做藉口，你話呢單野支那無份都無人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02