有的企業。<br />\n<br />\n面對西方制裁，官方傳媒引述國防軍總司令敏昂萊在政府會議上表示，要將精力投入在恢復身陷困境的國家經濟，必須採取補救措施，呼籲減少國家支出和進口，並擴大出口。他又說，警方正使用最低武力應對示威，例如橡膠子彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577068-20210223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577068-20210223.htm&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a5b64b62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577068-20210223.htm&h=432bc656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577068-20210223.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r3rgczveqeU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr3rgczveqeU&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=f08e968f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r3rgczveqeU</a>"},{"pid":"1306c49dc02d89f8aa7e5f76331998a35a9acc3b","tid":2419832,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4e4d83e237e8b599f18280e623e437ffc69eca","tid":2419832,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d1d9d493eb4d741fbf5c85ac0c130d79a32aed3","tid":2419832,"uid":279333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:55:55.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n咁撚熟面口<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撑狗遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T14:17:58.000Z","msg":"回帶咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\"